      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "AUTUMN LOVER (6) debuted in a much stronger race at Flemington in the Talindert Stakes, working home fairly well there behind a talented winner. The form held up well in the Blue Diamond and coming back to maiden grade here should see her very hard to hold out. LAGUNANINI (9) is a filly by I Am Immortal on debut for the Busuttin & Young stable. She draws well and has been jumping out well, winning her latest. Expect she goes well. COUNT CHEVALIER (2) is a gelding by Zousain for the Hayes yard on debut. The stable are good with their juveniles and he's won a jumpout. Respect. PIPERINE (3) is a gelding by King's Legacy on debut for the Eurell yard. He's won a jumpout here and will be running on strongly. BACKFLIPS (7) is a filly by Acrobat for the Price & Kent yard. Watch the betting.",
